      <title>铜攀登，因为新特朗普的关税据称是更衡量的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/metals-edge-higher-as-new-trump-tariffs-said-to-be-more-measured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，铜价上涨，因为交易者消化了唐纳德·特朗普的关税的迹象，其目标比预期的要高。]]></description>
